ctions in interplanetary space.\nWe propose that low cross helicity of fluctuations is added to the standard\nlist of ICME signatures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 May 2022 15:25:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-23"}
